        "rich_text_MxgxwF": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Lab Grown Diamond jewelry is stealing the spotlight globally, and youngsters are at the heart of this sparkling shift. From brides seeking unique cuts and vibrant colors to environmentally conscious consumers looking for ethical elegance, Lab Grown Diamonds are finally earning the love and attention they deserve. Affordable, sustainable, and stunningly real - these modern gems are reshaping how the world defines luxury, one sparkle at a time. Let’s dive deeper into why Gen-Z and Millennials are switching to Lab Grown Diamond Jewelry.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_VTHAhf": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Affordable Luxury Without Compromising On Beauty",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Affordable Luxury Without Compromising On Beauty</h2>",
            "custom_id": "affordable",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_9CwTgn": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Affordable_Luxury_Without_Compromising_On_Beauty.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Luxury is not about being inaccessible and expensive today. Luxury is now redefined, and focuses on craftsmanship, quality, values and individuality. The Gen-Z and Millennials are spending smartly on this luxury by investing in pieces that stand for their values - eco-friendly, conflict-free, and artistry. Studies show that these youngsters are twice as price conscious as older generations. The same trend can be seen in their spending on Lab Grown Diamonds India. These diamonds are physically, chemically, and even optically the same as naturally Mined Diamonds, except that naturally Mined Diamonds take a billion years to form. </p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_YQMHye": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Lab Grown Diamonds allow for more personalisation options - including the color of diamonds, making them classic yet trending across the world. <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lab Grown Diamond\">Lab Grown Diamond</a> price in India is 40-50% cheaper than naturally Mined Diamond jewellery, while being 100% real diamonds.<br/><br/>Choosing sustainable options is no longer a trending choice, but a much needed lifestyle habit. Reports confirm that 65% of consumers consider sustainability before making a luxury purchase. </p><p>Millennials and Gen Z are investing in beauty not just through the wider, more affordable choices in diamonds, but also by prioritizing sustainability and ethics.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_p8UXaz": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Certified Quality and Trust",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Certified Quality and Trust</h2>",
            "custom_id": "quality",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_dzwDHt": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Top_Reasons_Gen-Z_and_Millennials_Are_Switching_to_Lab_Grown_Diamond_Jewelry.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Today’s buyers want authenticity and transparency. In the jewellery industry, it is important to know the specifics of the product you are buying and the price breakdown. Along with hallmarked gold and platinum jewelry, diamonds should be certified. IGI and SGL are two such globally recognized gemological institutions </p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "aurefly-diamond-stud-earrings",
              "cotton-candy-hexagon-diamond-bracelet"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_WMcFka": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>that provide diamond certificates and are particularly popular for Lab Grown Diamond certifications. <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lucira Jewelry\">Lucira Jewelry</a> is a certified jewelry brand in India, with exemplary luxurious and versatile designs. At the core of our companies lies the value of being transparent to our consumer with a detailed breakdown of the price and quality of all Lab Grown Diamond online displayed on our website. We believe this is important for all our customers to make an informed decision when they are shopping for their milestones and grand celebrations. </p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_4kz8Th": {
          "type": "rich_text",
