        },
        "rich_text_HJrjyF": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p><a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-ring\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Engagement Rings\">Engagement rings</a> and wedding rings for couples need to reflect the couple’s style as well as values. Lab Grown Diamonds are the trending choice for couples as they are not only affordable, but also provide more value for money, while being sustainable. Men are proposing with rings for girlfriend that are made out of Lab Grown Diamonds, knowing that these real diamonds cost less and come in a bigger size with more flawless cuts and varied colors. Diamond <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/eternity-wedding-rings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Eternity Wedding Ring\">eternity wedding rings</a> are trending for the stunning array of diamonds, each beautifully reflecting light, with the prong setting that symbolizes everlasting love. In fact, Lab Grown Diamonds have opened a door to an increased variety of <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/wedding-rings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Wedding Rings\">wedding rings</a> for women. Rings set feature various diamond colors, carats, and shanks, with customizable metal color options such as rose gold, yellow gold and white gold or platinum. </p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_7Amx7F": {
