            "image": "shopify://shop_images/The_Perfect_Premium_Gifting_Choice.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Luxury gifting got easier with Lab Grown Diamond jewellery. You cannot go wrong with premium gifting when you choose diamonds as it looks luxurious and timeless while being affordable and real. Lab Grown Diamond <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-earrings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lab Grown DIamond Earrings\">earrings</a> are the perfect choice for gifts for women, whether you are looking for a luxurious gift for your mother, wife, girlfriend or close friends or relatives. </p>",
