        "rich_text_chjt9G": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Beyond Rings: Everyday Jewelry Choices",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Beyond Rings: Everyday Jewelry Choices</h2><p>Gone are days when premium jewelry was all about engagement and wedding rings! Accessorizing creates an impression of elegance, poise and grace in every movement while looking like statement pieces perfect for symbolizing milestones and celebrating grand moments. Gold bangle bracelets for women that are now beautifully crafted with Lab Grown Diamonds are trending across India for a layered, modern look. Whether you are looking for <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/hoop-earrings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Hoop Earrings\">hoop earrings</a>, sui dhaga or <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/dangles\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Dangles\">dangles</a>, Lab Grown Diamond Earrings are perfect for everyday luxury wear, crafted for every space from boardrooms to cafes. </p>",
            "custom_id": "everyday",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_RKEQND": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion </h2><p>Buying Lab Grown Diamond means choosing the environment, luxury, and trending yet timeless designs. At Lucira Jewelry, we make shopping for Lab Grown Diamond jewelry easier with insured and fast shipping, virtual assistance, price breakdowns, certified collections and phenomenal customer support and service. The jewelry landscape is undergoing a revolution with millennials and gen-z choosing trust, affordability and sustainability. We have entered this new era of truly beautiful diamonds where you can explore designs crafted to sparkle without any compromise.  </p>",
